data.description: Le'ts cozy up!  Looking for a perfect place to call home?  Our Cotton Creek awaits.    Every single space is Texas sized... kitchen, bedrooms, closets, pantry, game room, storage space and outdoor living... ALL VERY LARGE.  This is a must see home in a great, friendly neighborhood with amazing NISD schools that give your children the edge to succeed.  Cotton Creek's interior has been updated with paint and fixtures for move in ready status.  Easily add a couch in the enormous primary bedroom and get cozy after those long work days.  The size of the primary bedroom closet is also an added bonus, plenty of room for a dresser, a safe or custom build-ins; no problem.  Outdoor relax and entertain on your .17 acre greenbelt lot that boasts a $2k children's play fort, covered patio, extended slab with a fire pit.  Rare find in a great neighborhood.  MILITARY TRANSFER, PRICED TO SELL!  Will not last, schedule your visit today.
